            <div class="card card-pad"><h3 style="margin-top:0">Roadmap</h3><ul class="muted line-list"><li>v3.3.0: Assets Register, Advert Library and simplified object classification.</li><li>v3.3.1: Create Advert from image/logo/text/contact details and generate a PNG master.</li><li>v3.3.2: Fit-aware Advert Builder guardrails: font sizes, auto-fit and template sliders.</li><li>v3.3.3: Editable Advert Library: versioned PNG renders, editable design metadata and source-image reuse.</li><li>v3.3.4: Webmail outbound formatting: club branding moves from the top banner into the signature/footer.</li><li>v3.3.5: Advert Builder workbench layout: preview on the left, controls on the right, with independent control scrolling.</li><li>v3.3.6: Compact Advert Builder controls so more RHS settings remain visible while previewing.</li><li>v3.3.7: Asset Gallery / Asset Picker with duplicate image cleanup foundation.</li><li>v3.3.8: Article Library / controlled TinyMCE editor plus Assets Register 5×5 contact-sheet thumbnails.</li><li>v3.3.9: DOCX/email image controls, inline assets and A4 article layout preview.</li><li>v3.4.0: Place Article Library content directly into Issue Builder using vacant page real estate.</li><li>v3.4.1: Magazine Article Renderer foundation: TinyMCE alignment controls, justified two-column article pages, footer rule and issue/page metadata.</li><li>v3.4.2: Article Renderer refinement: controlled magazine blocks, image caption control, manual page breaks and pagination polish.</li><li>v3.4.3: Article Renderer pagination fix: two-column measurement, continuation-page placement and bottom-fill diagnostics.</li><li>v3.4.4: Article Renderer page preservation fix: generated page fragments survive editor saves and repeated slot headers are suppressed.</li><li>v3.4.5: Article Renderer restoration: hidden page-fragment payloads survive Issue Builder preview/editor refreshes.</li><li>v3.4.6: Article Renderer viewport stabilisation: no preview upscaling, no image CSS bleed-through, and less overfit flicker when toggling proof/editor views.</li><li>v3.4.7: Article Renderer whitespace reduction: pull-forward text fill and auto-shrink movable image blocks to avoid large blank page bottoms.</li><li>v3.4.28: A4 diagnostics always visible, hidden window measurement repaired, and trailing blank article candidates pruned after generation.</li><li>v3.4.29: Article image float layout modes: full column, float left and float right text wrapping.</li><li>v3.5.4: TinyMCE A4 composer containment; the A4 editor surface is fixed inside a controlled viewport instead of triggering infinite grey-area growth.</li><li>v3.4+: controlled HTML/CSS rendering, PDF export and merge pipeline.</li></ul></div>
